</div>
    </section>

    <!-- Biography Section -->
    <section id="biography" class="biography">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header">
                <center>
                <h1 style="color: darkblue;" class="section-title">Kalpana chawla's inspirational journey</h1>
                
                <p style="color:brown" class="section-subtitle">
                    From a small town in India to the vastness of space, Kalpana Chawla's journey inspires millions around the world.She first flew on the 
                    space shuttle "colombia"in 1997 as a mission specialist and "robotic arm"operator abroad.
                </p>
                </center>
            </div>
            
            <div class="biography-content">
                <div class="biography-cards">
                    <div class="bio-card">
                        <h3 style="color:blue" class="card-title">Early Life</h3>
                        <p style="color:brown" class="card-text">
                            Born on March 17, 1962, in Karnal, Haryana, India, Kalpana Chawla was fascinated by flying from an early age. 
                            She earned her Bachelor's degree in Aeronautical Engineering from Punjab Engineering College in 1982, 
                            becoming the first woman to graduate from the institution.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="bio-card">
                        <h3 style="color:rgb(172, 27, 56)" class="card-title">Academic Excellence</h3>
                        <p style="color:brown" class="card-text">
                            Kalpana moved to the United States in 1982 to pursue higher education. She obtained her Master's degree 
                            in Aerospace Engineering from the University of Texas at Arlington in 1984, followed by a Ph.D. in 
                            Aerospace Engineering from the University of Colorado Boulder in 1988.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="biography-image">
                    <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/jerrick/image/upload/c_scale,f_jpg,q_auto/64bfd556193c4a001d7a6f7e.jpg"
                         alt="Academic achievement representation" 
                         class="bio-img">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

